summary: Completed comprehensive testing of Coach Dashboard Profile pages with Account and Brand tabs. All core functionality verified including redirect, form elements, tab switching, data prefilling, validation, and localStorage persistence.
passed_tests: Account tab shows Edit Profile heading with all required elements
Account tab contains: avatar with edit button, first name, last name, about, DOB, gender, email fields
Account tab includes weight/height units (KG/LBS, CM/FT) with radio button selection
Account tab has SAVE CHANGES button
Brand tab shows Edit Brand heading with all required elements
Brand tab contains: logo placeholder with edit button, brand name, currency dropdown
Brand tab includes color theme picker with 24 color options
Brand tab has SAVE CHANGES button
Tab switching works correctly between Account and Brand tabs
Active tab styling shows underline indicator (text-slate-900 class)
First name and last name are prefilled from registration data (Test/Coach)
Brand name is prefilled from registration data (Test Brand)
Form validation shows error messages for required fields when empty
Color theme picker displays 24 colors in grid layout and is clickable
Avatar and logo edit buttons are present and clickable
Data persists via localStorage (moove_profile and moove_brand keys)
Authentication guards work properly (requires coach role)
Profile layout includes ProfileTabs component with proper navigation
